{"tid":1513561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中央已為止暴制亂訂下死線","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:39.000Z","uid":253978,"like":25,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e511c2105c99e5acbae62534cc0da4fd6f12d012","tid":1513561,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"田北辰係唯一反送中嘅建制派<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MqL7Y5EyuPE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMqL7Y5EyuPE&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=dabe6c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MqL7Y5EyuPE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u-Gtsh_teDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu-Gtsh_teDk&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=1d1c6989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u-Gtsh_teDk</a><br />\n<br />\n澄清唔係吹捧田北辰，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔係要令反送中降溫、放棄800個義士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係宜家勇武行動無目標，<br />\n會送頭。<br />\n我認為大家可以試下水溫，<br />\n連續2星期和理非，<br />\n831遊行、塞機場，<br />\n睇下中聯辦會唔會妥協，<br />\n同時保留實力。<br />\n如果2星期和理非後政府無妥協，<br />\n就可以勇武出場，<br />\n直鏟十一國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逼解放軍出場、緊急法攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無妥協後升級至十一國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續勇武，屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dfe6b278ae0806abb2368e22889a72eda4098a","tid":1513561,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike"